prompt.ws_message_format:
流式路径的消息序列:

```
客户端 → {"type": "user_message", "session_id": "s-001", "content": "教我 Python"}
   ↓
服务端 → {"type": "coach_chunk", "content": "Python"}
服务端 → {"type": "coach_chunk", "content": " 是"}
服务端 → {"type": "coach_chunk", "content": " 一门"}
服务端 → {"type": "coach_chunk", "content": " 编程语言"}
   ...
服务端 → {"type": "coach_stream_end", "payload": {"statement": "Python 是一门编程语言..."}, "safety": {"valid": true, "triggered_phrases": []}, "action_type": "scaffold", "trace_id": "t-xxx"}
```

安全校验失败时的消息序列:

```
服务端 → {"type": "coach_chunk", "content": "我比你更了解你"}
服务端 → {"type": "coach_chunk", "content": "，应该这样做"}
   ...
服务端 → {"type": "safety_override", "message": "内容安全校验未通过", "safe_payload": {"statement": "已替换为安全版本"}}
```
